---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Support | Windows Update Reset Tool">
  <main class="mx-auto my-0 max-w-screen-xl p-6 pt-16">
    <div class="mt-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-indigo-main">How can I help?</h1>

      <p class="mt-4 text-black">
        There are several ways you can contribute to improving our project. You
        don't have to be a developer to help! Some ways you can help include:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc">
        <li class="ml-8 mt-4 text-gray-dark">
          <strong class="text-black">Reporting errors</strong>: If you come
          across any mistakes in the documentation, please let us know. This
          helps us keep the documentation accurate and up-to-date.
        </li>

        <li class="ml-8 mt-4 text-gray-dark">
          <strong class="text-black">Requesting features</strong>: If you have
          an idea for a feature that would be useful, please propose it. We
          welcome feedback from our community and will take your suggestions
          into consideration.
        </li>

        <li class="ml-8 mt-4 text-gray-dark">
          <strong class="text-black">Correcting typos</strong>: If you notice
          any small errors, such as spelling or grammar mistakes, feel free to
          fix them. These may seem like minor issues, but they can make a big
          difference in the readability and professionalism of our
          documentation.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p class="mt-4 text-black">
        While we can't guarantee that every request will be implemented, we
        appreciate all feedback and take it seriously. Your suggestions and
        contributions help us make our project better for everyone. Thank you
        for your help!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-main">Other resources</h2>

      <ul class="list-disc">
        <li class="ml-8 mt-4 text-gray-dark">
          <strong class="text-black">GitHub</strong>:
          <a
            href="https://github.com/wureset-tools"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-main visited:text-purple hover:underline"
          >
            https://github.com/wureset-tools
          </a>.
        </li>

        <li class="ml-8 mt-4 text-gray-dark">
          <strong class="text-black">Docs</strong>:
          <a
            href="https://docs.wureset.com"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-main visited:text-purple hover:underline"
          >
            https://docs.wureset.com
          </a>.
        </li>

        <li class="ml-8 mt-4 text-gray-dark">
          <strong class="text-black">Status</strong>:
          <a
            href="https://status.wureset.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-main visited:text-purple hover:underline"
          >
            https://status.wureset.com/
          </a>.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
